1
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,679
There are animal remains everywhere down here.

2
00:00:36,679 --> 00:00:38,479
Probably where they handled offerings back then.

3
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:40,840
I think...

4
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,320
no matter what it was used for,

5
00:00:42,479 --> 00:00:43,359
the most important thing now

6
00:00:43,359 --> 00:00:44,640
is to find the altar.

7
00:00:44,719 --> 00:00:45,679
Stop dawdling.

8
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:54,039
This should be

9
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:55,719
the very end of this tunnel.

10
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:58,920
Could this be what Miss He mentioned,

11
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,320
the Eye of the Serpent God?

12
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,479
The Eye?

13
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:05,159
Hey, Chen,

14
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:07,359
how can you say this is the end?

15
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:10,159
Isn't this... isn't this the Eye?

16
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:15,319
A huge hole! Who triggered the mechanism?

17
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,599
Triggered the mechanism!

18
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,159
Looks... looks like it was me again.

19
00:01:21,319 --> 00:01:23,599
Fatty, you just can't keep your hands to yourself!

20
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,959
Stop touching things!

21
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:27,719
A massive hole!

22
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,280
A snake!

23
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,239
Fatty, close the door, quick!

24
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,840
Hard right! Hard right!

25
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:38,920
Right, right side!

26
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,920
Hard right!

27
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,000
Hard left!

28
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,200
Is this even working?

29
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:42,680
We're done for!

30
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:44,480
Lao Lu, don't panic, listen to me.

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,480
Shu Tong, you go over there.

32
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,560
Uncle Min, go that way.

33
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,599
Lao Lu,

34
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,879
go to the left rear.

35
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,480
Fatty, stay put and wait for my orders!

36
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,200
Got it.

37
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:08,479
All life and death are blessed by the Serpent God.

38
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:25,719
Shu Tong,

39
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:28,520
Lower left three, clockwise.

40
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,759
Upper right two, counterclockwise.

41
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:37,680
Upper right two, counterclockwise.

42
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,960
Lower right five, counterclockwise.

43
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,159
Lao Lu,

44
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,319
Lower right two, clockwise.

45
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,319
Fatty,

46
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,960
Lower left three, clockwise.

47
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,479
Did it open?

48
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,719
Commander Chen, not bad at all!

49
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:41,280
How did you know which way to turn each wheel?

50
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,759
And just like that, the thing opened.

51
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,360
Remember back in Nanyun?

52
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,360
My brain was stimulated by the Lingxiao Pearl,

53
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:47,719
and made precise calculations.

54
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,599
So your brainwaves got affected again, huh?

55
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:52,080
Just lucky.

56
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,080
An Xiang.

57
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:53,680
An Xiang!

58
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,039
Are you okay?

59
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:54,759
What's wrong?

60
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:55,759
I...

61
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,840
I...

62
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:58,400
My wound hurts a bit.

63
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,800
Chen Youxi.

64
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,599
What happened?

65
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,800
Bi Huaqiang.

66
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,080
What is it, boss?

67
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,240
Get me the medicine.

68
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,719
Right away.

69
00:04:11,719 --> 00:04:13,280
Let's go sit down up ahead.

70
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:13,879
Come on.

71
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,759
Okay, okay, you guys rest.

72
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,519
Lao Lu and I will scout ahead. Let's go.

73
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,959
Want to sit down and rest for a bit?

74
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,560
If we get through here,

75
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,079
we might just reach the end.

76
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:26,680
Weren't you anxious to uncover the truth?

77
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:29,399
But your body has to hold up first.

78
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,399
Don't worry.

79
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:32,360
I know what I'm doing.

80
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:33,240
But— Let's go.

81
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:20,879
So many eyeballs?

82
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,759
Brother Chen.

83
00:05:21,759 --> 00:05:23,800
So many eyeballs on the way in,

84
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,439
and so many on the way out.

85
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,000
I think

86
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,199
maybe we've hit a dead end.

87
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:29,879
Don't move!

88
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,279
With so many eyeballs around,

89
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,639
Why'd you have to touch it?

90
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:38,600
That's a trap.

91
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:42,120
Wait, I triggered a trap?

92
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,199
Listen, listen!

93
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:50,839
The countdown's started.

94
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,000
Then...

95
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,079
Don't let go!

96
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,160
The moment you release it,

97
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,000
arrows, crossbows,

98
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,519
mercury, sand,

99
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,920
who knows what'll come out.

100
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,560
We'll all be done for.

101
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,639
Then what am I supposed to do now?

102
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,000
Your right leg.

103
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,560
Lift your right leg up.

104
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,360
Higher.

105
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:11,040
I can't lift it anymore!

106
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,240
Try a little harder.

107
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,720
See that eyeball up there?

108
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:16,519
Lift your right foot and press it.

109
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,920
Press it.

110
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,040
Yes, yes, yes.

111
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,800
Right hand.

112
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,800
Right hand, come on, right hand.

113
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:29,120
And then?

114
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,160
Reach under your thigh, reach through.

115
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,759
There's an eyeball when you reach through.

116
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,040
Press it.

117
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,920
Got it.

118
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,240
Last step.

119
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:44,000
See that big round ball in the middle?

120
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,079
I see it.

121
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,720
Use your head.

122
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,680
Lean against the center eyeball.

123
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,560
Push, push!

124
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,959
Push harder!

125
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,519
I can't reach it!

126
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:00,079
Damn Fatty, what's in your hand?

127
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,439
It's a flash... flashlight.

128
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:03,959
Boss, you're messing with us!

129
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,240
Bi Huaqiang!

130
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:23,079
Just kidding.

131
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,720
Right.

132
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,959
No harm done.

133
00:07:28,279 --> 00:07:29,079
Brother Chen,

134
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,399
I'm just an old man.

135
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:33,720
Going ahead to clear the way for you,

136
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,040
that's only right.

137
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,319
It's no big deal.

138
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,639
The thing is, Brother Chen,

139
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,399
if there's no mechanism,

140
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:41,000
how do we get through?

141
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,000
I say, don't we still have explosives?

142
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,079
Just blow it open.

143
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,160
Blow it up, my ass!

144
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,759
If it triggers a cave-in,

145
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,800
could we even escape?

146
00:07:48,279 --> 00:07:49,399
Have some sense, would you?

147
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,639
If anyone gets blown up, it's you first.

148
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:52,360
Then how do you suggest we open it?

149
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:55,160
I've got a trick up my sleeve.

150
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:56,120
Listen up.

151
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,600
Commander Chen, please.

152
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,639
By the logic of the Mengnagu people,

153
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:06,040
the eight eyeballs represent the Bagua.

154
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,120
Which are divided into Yin and Yang,

155
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:10,120
the pupil is Yin, and the white is Yang.

156
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,519
Yin-Yang, Five Elements, Bagua,

157
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:13,480
those are things our ancestors left us.

158
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:16,079
The East Asian Confucian sphere.

159
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:16,920
Outside this sphere,

160
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,160
no other place could have Bagua.

161
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,720
Ancient civilizations' abstract worldviews

162
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,399
actually share common ground.

163
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,160
What's more, geographically,

164
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,560
exchange and contact were possible.

165
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,160
Tribal migrations can't be ruled out either.

166
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,759
So,

167
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,440
cross-regional similarities among ancient civilizations,

168
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,000
while uncommon,

169
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:37,279
have indeed occurred.

170
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:40,440
Miss He makes a valid point.

171
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,559
Moreover, when in one place

172
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:43,559
traces foreign to the local civilization appear,

173
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,759
it means this place has archaeological value.

174
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,600
Our presence here

175
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,879
takes on meaning.

176
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,919
This place

177
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:03,080
must be the Abyss Temple of Mengnagu.

178
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,360
According to the murals,

179
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:07,679
the Lingxiao Pearl

180
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,399
should be on the high platform at the stone altar's center.

181
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:47,840
What does this say?

182
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:54,080
Roughly, it means...

183
00:10:54,919 --> 00:10:57,840
All beings suffer, trapped in all directions.

184
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:03,519
Only by lighting the three lamps

185
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,080
will the sacred pearl reappear,

186
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,759
freeing us from all suffering.

187
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,519
The three lamps...

188
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,279
Where are they?

189
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,120
Three lamps.

190
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:20,759
Is it... is it that one?

191
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,360
That one!

192
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,240
And this one!

193
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:28,639
If so, hurry up and light them!

194
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:29,799
Stop messing around.

195
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,519
Let the Chief of Staff finish.

196
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:34,840
Earthly flames will eventually die out.

197
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:38,080
Only time and the universe

198
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,600
can last forever.

199
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:45,960
December 12th, twelve o'clock.

200
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,039
Isn't that today?

201
00:11:50,919 --> 00:11:52,120
That's seriously weird.

202
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,720
People from thousands of years ago...

203
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,840
how could they know

204
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:58,159
that we'd come here today?

205
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,159
This isn't our day to die, is it?

206
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,159
Our time is up!

207
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,559
Check your watch, what time is it?

208
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,240
Twelve forty.

209
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:10,240
My time of death has already...

210
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:10,919
passed.

211
00:12:11,159 --> 00:12:12,000
It's passed, it's passed!

212
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:15,200
Right, right, not dead. Great, great!

213
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,039
What do you mean?

214
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,080
Commander Chen!

215
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,399
Be... behind you!

216
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:47,639
Behind you!

217
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,600
Lao Lu!

218
00:12:59,039 --> 00:13:01,000
Lao Lu! Lao Lu!

219
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,120
Run!

220
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:12,679
This way, hurry!

221
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,759
Hurry up!

222
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,600
Did you trigger some mechanism just now?

223
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,240
An Xiang! An Xiang!
